oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六弟 破解心底怨萬重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧卡~ 古~ 光照見迷夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獌狗 千百種 糾結半生 未揭盅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回望這個費爵殺敵無數 被英超作弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每隻廢獌如像看通 又狂傲似瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成就世界最大縱被狂串 得失恥笑中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誰話我 攀不上巔峰 蘇B四大皆空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6354390ff3faedf53cb089e486575b055579f7","tid":1146324,"uid":69568,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"追返嗮成日嘅po 由今朝見到賽果到依家都好頹 明明撘咗件巴塞jacket喺凳都冇面着出街 考試都凝住冇咗個態咁 前排先盡情笑完身邊啲49000 就係因為根本冇諗過同樣嘅事會發生喺自己隊波身上 明明已經穩入決賽咁濟都可以自爆 今朝一路溫書一路睇波 睇住華dee on99咁 唔睇波衫以為我地先係揸兩球喺手嗰隊 到輸三粒先攻 士氣已經冇嗮 球員又攰 就算對港隊都入唔到啦 華dee臨場調動唔得 又串9主席 平時輪換又唔積極啲 聯賽不敗有獎? 下年可以直接入決賽? 就算係咪又係白白浪費咗小花同老伯一年 依家老伯走添啦 美斯都31 歐聯只會更家吃力 小花退休後更家唔敢想像...<br />\n我知我喺度資歷唔算深 只係捧咗巴塞11年 但係未試過好似今日呢一刻對自己對波咁失去信心 俾你今季本土雙料冠軍又點? 我根本見唔到巴塞膠層或者教練對夢二夢三過後嘅部處 有一兩年過渡期我接受到 但係之後呢? 你話買咗古同umtiti 咁青訓呢 過多一段時間佢地都會老 如果一路唔重視青訓 唔同一路𨂽錢每年買個丹返嚟?<br />\n今日呢場波我相信係巴區手足憤怒嘅爆發點 個個都屌爆華dee 但係無可否認佢係解決咗巴塞上兩季後防經常自爆嘅問題 不過正正可能防守呢樣係佢嘅足球哲學 真係唔適合巴塞進攻嘅踢法 佢可能係一個唔錯嘅教練 但係留喺度對巴塞同佢都唔會係一件好事<br />\n一時發洩打咗咁多字 我都係返去溫書先￼&nbsp;但係正如上面話齋 邊度跌低 邊度企返起身 我地唔係勝利球迷 我地係巴迷 我地捧嘅係巴塞 巴塞唔只係一間球會咁簡單 更加係一種信念 抵屌嘅應該大力屌 但係當球隊俾人笑嘅時候 都會企出嚟同人講 我為自己隊波感到自豪 依家雖然係喺低谷但係就算失望不能絕望 一日巴迷 一生巴迷 forca barca"},{"pid":"4119afaf75ca0abe9fb959f89efd434e0af5f4a6","tid":1146324,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb63ee2dabd9c01e6126750c1265570d839d690","tid":1146324,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fb178308befd9a727fdae2ca0ba57b9c60a4e3","tid":1146324,"uid":125070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ebb63ee2dabd9c01e6126750c1265570d839d690","tid":1146324,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"每隻廢獌如像看通 又狂傲似瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33f19d948f974200f9a270ad67caf945c2b18ee","tid":1146324,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fb178308befd9a727fdae2ca0ba57b9c60a4e3","tid":1146324,"uid":125070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ebb63ee2dabd9c01e6126750c1265570d839d690","ti